OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with a few spots
OL,6,Fof light rain possible at times. Cloud
OL,7,Fwill gradually start to break through
OL,8,Fthe morning to give some warm sunny
OL,9,Fspells across the region. Feeling
OL,10,Fpleasant in the sunshine with light
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA warm end to the day with
OL,14,Fsome late evening sunshine. Staying
OL,15,Fdry overnight with clear skies at
OL,16,Ffirst, but cloudier later. A cool
OL,17,Fnight for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
