OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy skies are likely at
OL,6,Ffirst during the morning, but quickly
OL,7,Fturning sunny by lunchtime with blue
OL,8,Fskies and light winds.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,11,FStaying largely dry with sunny spells
OL,12,Fand variable amounts of cloud. A few
OL,13,Fspots of rain are possible at times
OL,14,Fwhere the cloud thickens. Temperatures
OL,15,Faround the seasonal average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
